\n     5\t负责推荐卡片生成、滑动操作处理、双向匹配判定与通知。\n     6\t\n     7
\t## 流程图\n     8\t\n     9\t### 推荐卡片\n    10\t\n    11\t```mermaid\n    1
2\tsequenceDiagram\n    13\t    participant C as Flutter App\n    14\t    partic
ipant API as MatchingController\n    15\t    participant S as MatchingService\n 
  16\t    participant DB as MySQL\n    17\t    participant R as Redis\n    18\t\
n    19\t    C->>API: GET /matching/recommendations\n    20\t    API->>S: getRec
